      right: ["Complete facial paralysis (House-Brackmann VI) with no movement","Inability to close eye with corneal exposure and ulceration risk","Bilateral facial paralysis (consider Lyme disease, GBS, sarcoidosis)","No recovery after 6 months suggesting permanent nerve damage","Recurrent episodes requiring investigation for tumor or systemic disease"]
