      right: ["Respiratory arrest from combined benzodiazepine-opioid overdose","Status epilepticus from abrupt benzodiazepine withdrawal","Severe paradoxical agitation requiring emergency intervention","Neonatal withdrawal syndrome (jitteriness, poor feeding, seizures) from maternal use","Severe cognitive decline and functional impairment from chronic high-dose use"]
